{"tid":2441994,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"宮脇咲良有望加入 Big Hit！IZ*ONE 解散後動向引發關注","createTime":"2021-03-11T05:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T00:13:08.000Z","uid":16659,"like":11,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"544ba94be844093b01b1684772e4225b13ed3d20","tid":2441994,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:28:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_5120d2c21c5f84e2a7425f935ca75728/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-11/134189-899633.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_5120d2c21c5f84e2a7425f935ca75728%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-11%2F134189-899633.png&h=7a160851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nIZ*ONE 昨晚宣布將照原定時間解散後，12 位成員的未來動向立刻成為焦點，其中人氣超高的宮脇咲良（HKT48 成員）有望繼續在韓國活動！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據韓國媒體「韓國經濟」今日（11 日）透露的採訪結果，宮脇咲良在 IZ*ONE 的活動結束以後，將加入 Big Entertainment 繼續展開活動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_d1d008836e9ed8c0aebde8c4fc581f6a/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-11/134189-899632.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_d1d008836e9ed8c0aebde8c4fc581f6a%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-11%2F134189-899632.jpeg&h=1a4f3642&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_6dacf1fd77bc7d9058f6e9fe38f98546/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-11/134189-899634.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_6dacf1fd77bc7d9058f6e9fe38f98546%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-11%2F134189-899634.png&h=8de33cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多位韓國演藝圈相關人士表示，宮脇咲良最近向身邊的人透露將前往 Big Hit 一事，且日後很有可能加入 Big Hit 將推出的女子團體。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，Mnet 宣布 IZ*ONE 將照原定計畫，在本週末舉行兩天線上演唱會，並於 4 月結束長達兩年半的企劃活動。消息曝光後，也傳出部分成員希望繼續以小分隊形式合作，但確切情況仍有待各家經紀公司協調。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_52df08af95d8498aebb442d5cb8e681c/static.koreastardaily.com/2021-03-11/134189-899631.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_52df08af95d8498aebb442d5cb8e681c%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2021-03-11%2F134189-899631.jpeg&h=62e68aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（照片或影片來源：Off the Record、Big Hit Entertainment）"},{"pid":"a62741ace1ee94db5fb110dcf4ce34e44266f95e","tid":2441994,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:29:14.000Z","msg":"好on9喔！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f168fb982cbe3a38519ae7cde67122d3ed876bbb","tid":2441994,"uid":256796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:30:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d4b0e525261bd2acc1591abe882c6b38108ae84","tid":2441994,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a62741ace1ee94db5fb110dcf4ce34e44266f95e","tid":2441994,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:29:14.000Z","msg":"好on9喔！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"Shut the hell up!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd6e5d57f68fecc74b551d601456e38c10ab31a","tid":2441994,"uid":229026,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"佢去邊我跟去邊！"},{"pid":"f99766c8c761bd9d9b033c3a0c1fb6a1ab25e88c","tid":2441994,"uid":93096,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a62741ace1ee94db5fb110dcf4ce34e44266f95e","tid":2441994,"uid":256952,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-1